ices redtone provides a wide range of telecommunication services including prepaid and postpaid discounted call services to corporate customers and consumers as well as prepaid mobile airtime topup the company also offers prepaid shopping card services the company  s major subsidiaries during the years are illustrated as follows name   domicile and date of incorporation   effective ownership   principal activities redtone telecommunication china limited   redtone china     hong kong may        investment holding               redtone telecommunications shanghai limited   redtone shanghai     the prc july        provides technical support services to group companies               shanghai huitong telecommunication company limited   huitong      the prc march        marketing and distribution of ip call and discounted call services in the prc               shanghai jiamao ecommerce company limited   jiamao      the prc march        marketing and distribution of ip call and discounted call services in the prc               shanghai xin chang information technology company limited   xin chang      the prc january        marketing and distribution of ip call and discounted call services in the prc               vms technology limited   hong kong september        trading of discounted call related equipment and provision of related services               rt communications ltd   bvi february        investment holding               shanghai yuzhong financial information service co ltd   yuzhong      the prc july        investment holding               shanghai yuguang automobile inspection technology co ltd   yuguang      the prc july        investment holding               taizhou haitai motor vehicle inspection co ltd   haitai       the prc october        investment holding               feng cheng motor vehicle inspection co ltd   fengcheng      the prc november        dormant                    variable interest entities     f nantong jiatong hongsheng and qba were disp